Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.73,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\fnGill Sans Std ExtraBold Display\b1\c&HBDCACF&}H{\r}ow is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:39.76,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I feel a little lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:46.04,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Within the vast world,\Na single seed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:49.52,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}extended its roots
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:57.38,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}and put out a fruit\Nthat was still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:02.08,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fruit that I wish\Nwould turn orange soon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:05.16,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}is bathed in your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.90,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The ideals and dreams\Njust swell{\fscx300}-{\r}
