Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:14.20,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I wonder if someday the orange
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:15.76,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}will become sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:19.01,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Or will it wither away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.53,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I don't want to know\Nabout my future,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:24.76,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}so I ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:28.10,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}It's sour...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:36.71,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it, but I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:46.65,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fruit that I wish would\Nturn orange soon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:49.73,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}is bathed in your light.
