Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:00.44,ED English2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today, I tried eating an orange
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:03.69,ED English2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}but it was so sour I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.15,ED English2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I couldn't leave it behind like I have been,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:09.63,ED English2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}so I ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:12.96,ED English2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:16.41,ED English2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}It's Sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:19.95,ED English2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.95,0:23:25.01,ED English2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it... I love it.
