Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's snow everywhere! Everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery isn't bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but aren't these clothes a bit... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they're rentals, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a waste if we didn't try to have fun on this trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm just a natural skier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta, you're too cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm getting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pizza... Pizza...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't skied since middle school, but I guess I still have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minori-chan, you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a sports genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you're pretty good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just average.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:00:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm moving forward. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lean sideways according to the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sideways...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, getting run over by a sled hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why do you have a sled?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I wanted to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you can't ski?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so smug about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was the only one in our class who couldn't ski.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you can't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, skiing is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about wearing two long planks and sliding on snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was wondering too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask Kitamura to teach you how to ski?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell is he supposed to teach me when I have a sled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're not getting Minorin to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you're putting all my effort to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lift is for two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to share one with Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but shouldn't you share one with Kashii?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako and I want to take pictures of each other while we're on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why is that gal girl acting so friendly with Kitamura?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then get pissed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between you and Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! It's nothing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe something did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had tea with Kitamura-kun after I bumped into him on New Year's,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we went to visit a shrine for a New Year's prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So something like that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in bed with the flu, so you didn't need the extra trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do I need an excuse anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to report every single thing to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell do you always screw things up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always have to get in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really, really annoying{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's screwing things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You play weird tricks so you can hang around Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did, there's no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just want our friend to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:05:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I think your tricks are disgusting, and it pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn if an idiot like you gets pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.11,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's be nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a field trip, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of doing it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuusaku, are you thickheaded by nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or are you doing it on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to say something, just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I can't believe you're such an airhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nearly violent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the first day ended like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming Kushieda's real feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The field trip will be over before I even talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is so weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them, they look so lethargic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura didn't mention anything about visiting the shrine with Taiga to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly don't get what's going on in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sighing get!{yes this makes no sense, but this is what she says - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I saw you leave the dining hall all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've been waiting for a chance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noto-kun and Maya-chan were fighting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to relieve the tension between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a field trip, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want people to be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought the exact same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the problem is that Maya-chan wants to be around Kitamura-kun, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one view of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, do you know why Noto-kun wants to stop Maya-chan's love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he misunderstood and thinks that Taiga likes Kitamura-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he wants to help Taiga, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are things about Taiga that you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it's a treasure, so I'm going to really cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm talking about the hair clip, not myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use no matter how hard I try...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they call reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda can't accept my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of what happened on Christmas Eve, or of my one-sided feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she pretends that it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're worried about you, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, are you really asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kitamura, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking your clothes off all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.11,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only undressing your bottom part! How perverted are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all, you're waving it on top of Takasu's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it anymore. There's some mysterious gas in my butt... {split the adio... where?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You assholes!{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-By Kushieda, you mean {\i1}that{\i0} Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other Kushiedas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's Kushieda Minori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in love with that weird girl for over a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was rejected on Christmas Eve before I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did Kushieda reject you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a girl, I would definitely go out with Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, going out with you would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Taka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's like what happened in Chushingura.{this one might be a bit too hard to TL note, perhaps just provide a URL like http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ch%C5%ABshingura - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Asano Takumi-no-kami, and we're the Akou Ronin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and Kushieda is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kira is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.19,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I even rented the DVDs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kitamura is using me as an excuse to take revenge on the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door was unlocked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, why is it so messy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, control yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tidy it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a navy blue camisole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a wet towel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you had a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tolerate an odd number of socks, so I'm pairing them up to make them even.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Taiga of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she wipe the tatami with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't wipe your hair with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Taiga come back first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, no one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only time I've ever begged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That felt great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, you love taking baths, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ami-chan, your curves are great! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanted to be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Taiga go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came back to the room first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:48.56,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Taiga went to the guys' room by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be together with Maruo and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, you're overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be possible for Yuusaku to walk in on her and Takasu-kun doing stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were real, I would totally hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I wonder what's going on in Taiga's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really interested in Maruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Between Takasu-kun and Maruo, which one do you think is Taiga's favourite?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be troublesome for me to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ask Taiga herself when she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, you've been pretty quiet since we got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm tired from skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been sleepy since we got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't count on getting any sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have a girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Takasu-kun could get Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would make all these problems disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Minori-chan was dragged into her sea of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is relevant to my interests!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you heard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something I shouldn't have because you were spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't just stare at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and tell us, Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Maya-chan has said that, what should I do, Minori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you rejected Takasu-kun before he could confess on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Did Takasu-kun confess to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ami-chan, how do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, how do I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amin, why did you bring that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're always spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying it to spite you because it seems you don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun is interested in you, not Taiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you rejected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're just pretending to be an airhead so you can just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably thinking "Let's just be friends forever".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you see me pretending that nothing has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you look into my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so it has nothing to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your sense of guilt is nothing too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you at least had some feelings for Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you rejected him because you thought you'd feel guilty about {\i1}someone{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rejected him simply because you don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell him about it tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'd be kinder to just end it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than to leave him half-dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, should I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good at faking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we all arguing on a field trip?{orig: why are we girls arguing on a field trip? - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you went a bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just apologise, and let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Taiga isn't back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's look for her together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kushieda, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we just witnessed something that we shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and Kushieda was a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only one who doesn't get what they were arguing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which country was Ami-chan talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taka-chan, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we neither saw nor heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired, so I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to apologise for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be my fault that Minori-chan rejected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something sarcastic to Minori-chan when you weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know why I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I had an argument with Minori-chan yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt pissed off whenever I saw her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because she never looked directly into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I pushed her, I couldn't find out how she really feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you because you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself because I'm an idiot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt really guilty, and I exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of misunderstandings, and now it's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Chi', move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I told you to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times are you going to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologised already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you some ice cream when we get back to the dorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amin, I'm sorry for not stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sorry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it on purpose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that you did it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... I really couldn't stop{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't forgotten about what happened yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to mess things up because I was having a chat with Takasu-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By "what happened yesterday", you mean the thing you started?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I forgot about it you went and brought it up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.91,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you forgot about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been ignoring me all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your egotistical gaze pisses me off, you brainless Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's egotistical?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just pissed off because you're jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No hitting the face, Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't want to be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always hated people like you!{org: I've always hated those of your kind - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.64,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a follow-up on yesterday's argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there and watch, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, you're not yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:36.73,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the ski resort's staff are out looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can't find her, they're going to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip on yourself, they'll definitely find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it might be you who'll{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back when I've checked the places we've been to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, tell the teacher we're going out to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some skid marks down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get some adults over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left her alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has always been by my side, but I never noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That clumsy girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let go of you when I catch you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji would definitely save me at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Broken Hearts' blessing didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish didn't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take these feelings away from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...loving Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she pick me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a player!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that's not true, sorry.
